Dockerized Go Present Tool
Sample Presentation
25 Feb 2015
Tags: docker, golang, present

Michael Boudreau

* Running Direct

	docker run -v /mylocalslides:/app mkboudreau/docker-present 


* Baking Slides

- Put Dockerfile with slide source

	# Dockerfile contents
	FROM mkboudreau/docker-present:latest-onbuild

- Build/Bake image

	docker build -t <yourrepo>/<yourtag> .

- Run your baked presentation

	docker run <yourrepo>/<yourtag>
